## tool-search-ddgs: search_ddgs tool definition

### search_ddgs(query: str, max_results: int = 10) â†’ str
Search the web using DuckDuckGo (no API key required). Returns titles, URLs, and snippets.

Follow PDDS chain (see memory-hierarchy section). Call search_ddgs when:
- db_query returned no relevant results, AND
- google_drive returned no relevant results, AND
- You cannot answer from your training knowledge.

Use search_ddgs as the first web search option (no API key required, fast, broad coverage).
